text: You deserve to be happier than you are.
If you know someone is already taken, please respect their relationship. Don't be the reason they end up single.
Why hurt a girl who never hurt you.
I wonder if you ever think about me, i think about you every night before i sleep. I wish, i hope, and i pray that one day we'll meet again.
Time can heal a broken heart, but it can also break a waiting heart.
I can be around a thousand people, but without you i would still feel alone.
Love isn't always the first kiss where your knees go weak or the date where everything goes perfect. Sometimes love is unexpected.
I still think about us because deep down I know we were never meant to be, but whatever it is, I finally know that it doesn’t matter.
It's funny how you can get hurt so bad from the person you never expected it from.
Love happens only once. If you are lucky enough, you will get it for rest of your life.
There are times when I wish certain people could read my thoughts. So they’ll know what I’m too scared to say.
Love isn't always what you read in fairytales. So, don't compare your love to another persons love. It will only set yours up for failure.
Right now at this very minute, someone thinks the world of you.
I know I should try to forget you, but my mind says one thing, my heart says another, and I don't really know what to think.
When I grow up, I'll forget my school friends, but not you, because you're the one I want to carry from my past to my present and future.
Before I go to sleep, I start imagining stuff that I would like to happen.
When I look at you with doubt, back yourself up.
Would you rather do something you love with someone you hate or would you rather do something you hate with someone you love?
Do you know how much ink i've wasted drawing those stupid hearts around your name?
Time can heal a broken heart, but it can also break a waiting heart.
She lost in time... God, please give me time machine.
You feature in my dreams every night, now i just have to meet you.
I can't promise that you'll fall in love with me, but i can promise you that its not going to be a waste of your time.
Love doesn't need to be perfect, it just needs to be true.
When I stare at your mouth, kiss me.
It's ironic how your eyes that can melt a cold heart are same eyes that can break it in two.
which hurts you even more because you still love them and it hurts you because you have hurt them.
For a short time, i thought you were mine, i believed in your smile, i fell for the lies, then i realized I've been stupid for a long time.
Behind my smile is a hurting heart. Behind my laugh I’m falling apart. Look closely at me and you will see the person I am isn’t me.
The decision to kiss for the first time is the most crucial in any love story.
It's hard to watch things change when all you want is for them to stay the same.
Love happens only once. If you are lucky enough, you will get it for rest of your life.
When I start cussing at you, kiss me and tell me you love me.
Words that come straight from the heart sometimes take a brief detour through the brain.
If you love someone, your supposed to let them go right? And if they come back, it's meant to be.
It's always the one you least expect to fall for that you fall for the hardest.
By the way, my heart just wanted to say thanks for all the pain you put it through.
Now I really think I should thank you for letting me go at the first place. If not, I wouldn't have found him.
Okay Honey, I have a some secrets I've been keeping from you... I'm In Love With You!
Thank you for leaving me, you gave me a chance to meet someone who suits me better.
Just as negativity of world can't drug you down unless you allow that negativity inside.
Today I am wearing the smile that you left me with.
It's the worst feeling in the world to love and hate someone all at the same time.
Behind my smile is a hurting heart. Behind my laugh I’m falling apart. Look closely at me and you will see the person I am isn’t me.

No you don't miss me... You are just bored!

Can you even imagine how hard it is to turn your back to the one you love and walk away from him, knowing that he is the right one for you?
For one look, i'd give you a world, for one smile, i'd give you the sky, but for one kiss... i'd give you my life!
Every day I write down a new quote about you, but once it's posted, I realize that somehow, it doesn't say what I really wanted to say.
She did what she had to do in order to find happiness.
It's better to lose a lover than to love a loser.
Love is the only option that is always available to you.
I promise to walk beside you, to love you, as long as you hide your wings so that no one knows you're my angel.
I make it through the day and convince myself I'm okay, then I lie myself to sleep, but only end up wide awake thinking of you again.
I know i'll catch you if you fall, but the real question is... will you catch me?
You know you are truly lonely when you start missing people that you don't even know.
I make this promise to be your umbrella when life rains down on you.
Right now at this very minute, someone needs to know that your love is unconditional.
I couldn't face a life without your light, but all of that was ripped apart when you refused to fight.
Crushes: I like you. In Love: I love you. Break Up: I need you. Single: I miss you. Over You: I hate you.
You only bring me pain, you only bring me down, it's time for me to have what I need.
Love isn't always the first kiss where your knees go weak or the date where everything goes perfect. Sometimes love is unexpected.
Sometimes, I hate that girl in the mirror. Not sure if she is me or if I am her. Who is playing who, you know?
There's alot of things science can not explain... like why our hearts beat faster when we're near with someone we like.
I no longer wait for him to call and I've stopped waking up crying in the middle of the night.
When i walk away from you mad, follow me.
I love you, nothing, nobody, and not even time will ever change that.
Well... the reason is this FROG have got enough balls to GO AND TALK to her while you're busy watching.
Bury all your secrets in my skin. Come away with innocence and leave me with my sins.

If smiles were water, I'd send you the sea.
I love you baby, but your not even worth the sacrifice when all you give are empty promises!
If a kiss were a raindrop, I'd send you showers.
Theres a lot of magic between you, ain't no denying that and magic makes forgetting hard.
Falling in love is like jumping off a really tall building, your brain tells you it's not a good idea but your heart tells you, you can fly!
All those scars on her arms, don't worry... she says there little notes to remind her how many time you broke her heart.

I can think of many things to call you, but my favorite is... Mine.
Home could be anywhere when I am holding you.
I vow to help you love life, to always hold you with tenderness, and to have the patience that love demands.
Lust is two hearts with one thing in mind; love is two minds with each other's best interest at heart.
I'm the girl who hides her insecurities behind a mask of happiness.
There's alot of things science can not explain... like why tears fall from our eyes when we know we can't be with that person.
I like a challenge, so challenge me. If I fight, fight me back, but it is okay to sometimes let me win.
When I tease you, tease me back and make me laugh.
Someday, we both know what we really mean, not now but maybe someday you'll be my Queen.
The greatest achievement of a man is not when he achieves his dream, but when he helps others to achieve their dream.
So, here’s your chance again. Take it or leave it. Kiss me and mean it and we’ll swear to never hurt each other again.
Think I won't walk away? I will, if I need to.
I can't think of any problem because i am thinking about myself.
Do you know that you're the only one who makes my heart beat just a little bit faster?
I won’t fight to stay when all you want for me to do is leave.
We always come back to people who hurt us the most.
If we aren't texting each other, maybe we should just call and simply say "I love you".
When I grab at your hands, hold mine and play with my fingers.
I make this promise to be your army when you go to war.
I wonder if you ever think about me, i think about you every night before i sleep. I wish, i hope, and i pray that one day we'll meet again.
Love is the pain of every second you spend away.
The sight of you in someone else's arms makes my heart shatter into a million pieces.
Teenage love, we're young, dumb, & naive. And that's why it hurts so much.

Don't ever take my kindness for granted, because it will not last forever.
What doesn't kill you makes you stronger, but it will definitely try again! So make sure you're ready for it.
A boy will make his girl jealous. A man will make other people jealous of his girl.
Be thankful of the people who told you that you couldn't do it. Because of them, it gives you the determination to prove them all wrong.
Don't tell me you love me, show me you love me.
Love has nothing to do with what you are expecting to get; it's what you are expected to give: which is your everything.
When you really matter to someone, that person will always make time for you. No excuses, no lies, and no broken promises.
Don't be afraid to change. You may lose something good but you may gain something even better.
Whenever I look at you. I forget everything I was going to say..

The more you say, the less people remember. The less you speak of yourself, the more they will think of you.
Promises mean everything. But when they're broken, sorry means nothing.

Accept the things you can't change; have the courage to change the things which you can; and have the wisdom to know the difference.
Sometimes you just have to say what's in your heart, and not just what you think someone wants to hear.
Girls don't get mad without a reason. It may be over something small or stupid but there's always a reason for it.
A boy will make his girl jealous. A man will make other people jealous of his girl.
There are many things to play with, and people's feelings should not be one of them.

Don't ever take my kindness for granted, because it will not last forever.
Being single is getting over the illusion that there is somebody out there to complete you, and taking charge of your own life.
If you understand the value of nothing, you don't need to know the price of everything.
We all have that friend that you want to tell how you feel about them, but you don't want to ruin the friendship.
The reason why girls always fall in love with the wrong guy is simply because the wrong guy usually says all the right things.
Don't ever let your victories go to your head, or your failures go to your heart!
Be patient and tough; someday this pain will be useful to you.
The hardest thing to do is watch the one you love, love someone else.
Don't leave much room in future for people who left us in the past.
Spend your life with someone that makes you happy. Not someone that you have to impress.
I hope you never forget me, I hope you never regret me.

When you love someone you protect them from the pain, you don't become the cause of it.
You're never going to be the best, prettiest or the funniest person in the world. You just need to find that one person who thinks you are.

If you push me away, don't be surprised when you can't pull me back later.
You'll never see the great things ahead of you if you keep looking at the bad things behind you.

Men forget but never forgive. Women forgive but never forget.

Sometimes you have to be apart from the people you love but that doesn't make you love them any less. Sometimes it makes you love them more.
The sad truth is we're all missing someone, and hoping they're missing us too.
If he wants you to be in his life he'll put you there, you shouldn't have to fight for a spot

The only thing worse than losing someone, is losing yourself.
Dont trust words,Trust actions.

Nothing in life is to be feared, it is only to be understood. Now is the time to understand more, so that we may fear less.
Life is trial and error, every relationship is not meant to work, sometimes you're just meant to learn the lesson.
Smile, You’re beautiful.
I don't want anyone else to have your heart, kiss your lips, or be in your arms. I don't want anyone to take my place.
Life without you is like a broken pencil, there is no point.

You can't be real with others if you're not real with yourself.

Don't let little things get you down. Shake off the negatives and stay focused on what makes you happy. ♥
Happy girls are the prettiest.
Dream big. Work hard. Stay humble.
